{"tid":2307682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線中國組全體總辭","createTime":"2020-12-01T10:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T11:20:56.000Z","uid":348984,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c717338f3606bcd842638c308c28891f90c5ea","tid":2307682,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"香港有線電視新聞部裁員，中國組不滿決定全體總辭。<br />\n<br />\n中國組的助理採訪主任黃麗萍同樣在裁員名單之列，她批評高層完全無就裁員決定和部門主管商量裁員。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視中國組助理採訪主任黃麗萍：「但高層都是無底線的，我們都要學習近平所言，有個底線思維，去到不能忍受的地步，我們都需要作出我們的決定。」"},{"pid":"d6040db6e4b70f6f8bc527c6aa3c9946159f3e83","tid":2307682,"uid":108347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"其實要成個新聞部先有用,中國組係另一個共產炎最憎的組別,而家自己走埋佢仲開心"},{"pid":"c570487b2f689a9954e63da5832fb9ec6f33da3d","tid":2307682,"uid":45215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"點都好支持左先"},{"pid":"9cda91a64adc7aae27dddaa76856b538c73893ba","tid":2307682,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3966f745bb69be052d2ae809444d78a45ebbbb","tid":2307682,"uid":255624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8c00f74faf51c93f85dbce9c821a7e69282700","tid":2307682,"uid":348984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdb32af31ad97e4f22e51fb9a882a286f1a1f38","tid":2307682,"uid":258340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:11:53.000Z","msg":"［零成本］聲援有線！ 無人講？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2307531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2307531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3758129